description: Conventions for Helmfile components deployed via Atmos
globs: components/helmfile/**/*.yaml
alwaysApply: false
---

# Helmfile Conventions

- Access Atmos vars via `.Values` (e.g. `{{ .Values.chart_version | default "1.0.0" }}`)
- Always set `createNamespace: true`, `wait: true`, `timeout: 300`
- Always define resource requests and limits for all containers
- For Azure Workload Identity pods: annotate service account with `azure.workload.identity/client-id` and add `azure.workload.identity/use: "true"` pod label
- Each Helmfile component needs a matching catalog at `stacks/catalog/helmfile/{name}.yaml`
